Alimbitsa mtima wanga teretu.

Mtima 'we siya ndi Yesu nsonizi,
Usabisa tchimo lakoli;
Zichuluka mphamvu zakezi,
Likusunga dzanja lakeli;
Bwera kwa Mbuyathu leroli mwana 'we,
Bwera kwa Mbuyathu leroli mwana 'we.

Ndi ine sizitheka 'yi
Kuchoka zakuipazi;
Ndisambe m'mwazi wanuwo;
Ndagonjatu Mbuyamba 'Nu.

M'manja mopanda kanthu,
Mtanda ndingogwiradi;
'Maliseche mbveke 'ne;
Ndili ndekha, msunge 'ne;
Ndithawire m'mtsinjewo.
Munditsuke m'mtimamo.

Tadza kukudyaku,
Kwakonzedwatu;
Mkate wamoyodi,
Idyatu 'we;
Bwera wochimwanso,
Yesu adikatu,
Akuitanaku;
Mvetsatu 'we.

Yamba ulendowo
Wonka Kumwamba;
Pano mpoipatu
Padzikoli;
Komwe tikondwako, 
Tidzasekeranso tinke
Kumwambako;
Idzatu 'we.

Iwe tiye, iwe tiye,
Tiye tsopanoli;
Pano tiye kuli Yesu,Tiye tsopanoli.

Ambuye Yesu, Inutu
Munabadwira anthu 'fe;
Munatifera tonsefe;
Tiyamikira Inutu.

Mzimu Woyera, m'mtimamo
Tiyeretsedwe ndinutu;
Munatisunga bwinoli;
Tiyamikira Inutu.

Nditamatu Ambuyangayu,
Moyo wanga wonse ndidzamtamatu,
Ndiponso m'dziko lakumwambako;
Masiku anga onse ndidzamlemekeza Iye;
Sindidzaleka konsekonse m'mene ndili m'moyotu,  
Padziko pano pena m'Mwambamo.

Ndiye wokondwa, E, munthuyo  
Wokhulupirira Mlungu yekhadi,  
Wolenga dziko, nyanja, zonsezi;  
Choona chake chonse  chingokhalatu chosatha;
Apulumutsa onse namadyetsa anthu akewo,
Wokonda ndiye Mbuye wathuyo.

