Ndi maso Ambuyathu
Apenyetsetsa ife;
Amadalitsa onse
Okhulupirira Iye;

Amamva timbalame,
Namveka dziko lonse;
Sataya tizilombo,
Asunga zina zonse.

Yesu ponong'oneza, idzanitu;
Mupempherera ife, idzanitu;
Mupempherera ife, idzanitu;
Yomdziwa Mpulumutsi, idzanitu.

Imfa idzafika msanga;
Ndipo mdzaikidwa m'manda;
Nthawi yomwe simudzamva
Kuitana kwakeko.

Zonse zinathedwadi;
Yesu watha zonsezo;
Sutha ntchito, ungomvera
Mawu ake omwewo.

Mbuye wanga ndilikumva,
Ndikondana nanu;
Umapuma mzimu wanga;
Kwathu ndiko kwanu.

Lero lino ndi labwino;
Moyo wako uli nawo;
Pena m'mawa umwalira,
Udzatani mlandu wako?

Iwetu afuna,
Inde, kalelo;
Leronso adika
Mbuye wathuyo.
Uza Iye zonse
Za uchimowo;
Yesu ati leroli;
"Wachedwa 'we."

Yesu alindira,
Inde, iwetu;
Idza ndi kukhala 
Ndi chimwemwenso
Ku mikono yake
Yachikondiyo;
Sankha Iye msangatu;
Wachedwatu.

Inu nonse obvutidwa,
Mbuye ali panopa;
M'maso mwanu muli msozi;
'Dzani kwa Mbuyathuyo.

Ambuye wathu Yesu
Akhala Mfumunso;
Zoipa zazikulu
Azigonjetsa 'Ye;
Anena mawu ake
Ochotsa zonsezo,
Kalelo nalamula;
Pakhale bata duu!

Chikondi cha Mbuyathu
Chiposa zonsetu;
Chisomo chake chomwe
Chikondweretsabe;
Ulemu wake wonse
Umapambanadi;
Tiyeni, tikondwere
Popita m'Mwambamo.

Mukonze mtima wangawu,
Ndi zofuna zakezo.
Muyere ndithu m'katimo;
Ndilinda tere, Mzimu 'Nu,
Mupatsetu chikondicho;

Ndilira Mzimu leroli,
Mutsimikize Mawuwo;
Ya Mbuye Yesu mphamvuyi,
Ikhale yathu, yanganso;

Idzani, Mzimu Inu,
Mundidalitse kuno;
Ndafoka mtima ine
Polendo wanga uno;
Kwambiri ndakhumudwa
Panjirayo ya moyo;
Mkaleka kutsogola 
Ndiwonongeka pompo.

Wakunga mwana ine,
Sindidziwitsa konse;
Mundilandize Mzimu;
Panjira yanga yonse; 
Mundiyendetse bwino
Ndifike ine ndemwe
Panjira yolungama,
Kudziko lachimwemwe.

Mundilimbitse m'mtima
Pogwira ntchito izi;
Ndikapumula pena
Mukhale ndithu ndine;
Zolingirira zanga
Ziyere zonse m'mtima;
Zoipa muzichotse,
Sindidzazichitanso.

Tamani mphamvu ya Yesu,
Angelo agwade;
Tulutsanitu korona,

Tifuna kuti komweko
Tikamgwadire 'Ye;
Tidzaimba kosaleka;

Konda dzinalo la Yesu
Mwana wosauka 'we;
Ndilo lothandiza anthu;
Khala nalo ponse phee!

Kwa Mulungu m'Mwambamo
Amapempherako;
Chikondi chakenso
Chikhala chosatha;
Ndi mwaziwo
Akhalatu Wansembe wanga Yesuyo.

Ndiye mtsamiro 
Pogona ine;
Pofika kufa
Andidzutsanso;
Podzichepetsa
Andikwezanso;
Moyo wa moyo,
Yesu Ambuye.

Ndikakhumudwa 
Andilimbitsa;
Ndikadzitama 
Andichepetsa;
Ndikasokera;
Andilondola;
E! Wokondedwa
Yesu Ambuye.

Lambira Yesuyo
Wokonda tonsefe;
Mabala ake achikondi aonekabe;
Tisaiwale 'yi zowawa zakezo,
Tileke kumchimwira, kumsautsa Yesuyo.

Mbuye mabala anu olimba
Atichotsera mantha a imfa;
Tsono ndi mtima wonse tiimba;
Aleluya!

"Sezani mtanda wanuwu."
Musaopsedwe nawotu;
Mphamvu za Yesu nzanunso;
Limbani mtima wanuwo.

Pakuwoloka mtsinje wa imfa
Dzanja Mbuyathu agwira; 
Tikadagwira ntchito zake
Atipatsatu korona;
Komwe kulibe masauko,
Pena misozi maliro;
Mulungu tidzamtamandira,
Inde kosalekezanso.

Here I raise my Ebenezer;
Here by Thy great help, I've come;
And I hope, by Thy good pleasure,
Safely to arrive at home.
Jesus sought me when a stranger,
Wandering from the fold of God;
He, to rescue me from danger,
Interposed His precious blood.

Mbuye ndamva mwawazira
Anthu ena madalitso;
Mvula yanu yawagwera;
Mbuye, ine mudalitse.

O come, let us adore Him;
O come, let us adore Him;
O come, let us adore Him, Christ, the Lord!

God of God, Light of Light,
lo, He abhors not the virgin's womb;
very God, begotten not created;

O holy Child of Bethlehem,
descend to us, we pray;
cast out our sin and enter in;
be born in us today.
We hear the Christmas angels,
the great glad tidings tell;
O come to us, abide with us,
our Lord Emmanuel!
